          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Responsible Opioid Prescription Act</b></p> <p>This bill&nbsp;limits Medicaid coverage of&nbsp;opioids prescribed to enrollees other than those who are in long-term care facilities or who are receiving hospice care, palliative care, or treatment for cancer. <br /></p> <p><br /></p>]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
